name: La-water-and-power
tagline: This map shows residential power and water use averages in Los Angeles zip codes.
body:
Los Angeles residential water and power use.


This map shows the average monthly water and power used in Los Angeles zip codes.  The data is from Los Angeles County open data portal and spans 2005-2013.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
